    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "DATE: 12/28/48",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, Houston",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISC - [REDACTED] Complainant 67c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Attention: Assistant Director D.M. Ladd",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Remytel 12/28/48 in the above captioned matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "For the Bureau's information, on 12/27/48 [REDACTED] an attorney with offices",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Houston, Texas, telephonically contacted the Houston",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Office to advise that he had a friend, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "who had some information on an object which might be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "a flying disc. Mr. [REDACTED] stated he was calling in 67c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "response to Mr. [REDACTED] suggestion and as a means of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "determining what authorities would have an interest",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "in this matter. He said Mr. [REDACTED] was a machinist",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "employed by the [REDACTED] Houston.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] in calling, advised that the disc, or",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "object, was approximately eight feet in diameter, had a 67c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "tail and wings, and apparently was equipped for jet",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "propulsion. He stated [REDACTED] had observed this object",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "at a desert location near Las Vegas, Nevada; further,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "that Mr. [REDACTED] had taken some movie film of the disc and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "that this film was currently in his possession.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Immediately upon receipt of the above information,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED], Special Agent, O.S.I., Ellington",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Field, Texas, was notified as was true of Captain [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "[REDACTED] MID representative, also Houston. As a result of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "these referrals, arrangements were effected with Mr.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "[REDACTED] to bring his film to the Houston Office for a showing",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "at 5 P.M., 12/27/48. This was done with Messrs [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "[REDACTED] and Special Agent [REDACTED] and 67c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "the writer observing. Arrangements were then made for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] to again appear at the Houston Office on the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "morning of 12/28/48 in order that his information might be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "reduced to writing. Mr. [REDACTED] in making his initial",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "appearance at the office surrendered his movie film which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "consisted of one 50 foot roll of 8 mm movie film. Approximately",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "fifteen feet of this roll relates exclusively to the pictures",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "of the flying disc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "1-4-49",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
